But I think he was forced to take it since his wrist has a strap mark.

28
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:15,290
You mean it was a foul play.

29
00:02:15,290 --> 00:02:20,230
Yes. Aigoo. He must've been in pain the moment he died.

30
