- Ms. Seo Jae Won.

40
00:03:38,780 --> 00:03:40,230
Hold her.

41
00:03:40,230 --> 00:03:43,630
You're under arrest for the murder of Heo Sun Yeong.

42
00:03:43,630 --> 00:03:47,510
You have the right to remain silent. You have the right to an attorney.

43
00:03:47,510 --> 00:03:51,390
