530
00:48:22,850 --> 00:48:25,930
I can't always be next to her.

531
00:48:26,750 --> 00:48:29,610
I don't know how the situation would change, either.

532
00:48:33,510 --> 00:48:34,880
Please?

533
00:48:40,810 --> 00:48:43,510
Are you in a bad mood today, Ah Rin?

534
00:48:43,510 --> 00:48:45,590
Did something happen?

535
00:48:46,580 --> 00:48:48,160
No.

536
00:48:50,060 --> 00:48:52,020
Just tell me.

537
00:48:52,020 --> 00:48:53,820
What happened?

538
00:48:54,820 --> 00:48:57,160
- The thing is...
- Yeah.

539
00:48:57,160 --> 00:49:03,850
My teacher said your wish would come true if you prayed to the supermoon.

540
00:49:03,850 --> 00:49:08,840
So, I prayed as hard as I could without even sleeping.

541
00:49:08,840 --> 00:49:11,570
But it didn't come true.

542
00:49:12,570 --> 00:49:16,640
I see. So, you were upset.

543
00:49:16,640 --> 00:49:19,530
What did you pray for, Ah Rin?

544
00:49:19,530 --> 00:49:20,890
Tell me.

545
00:49:21,680 --> 00:49:24,470
I'll make sure it comes true.

546
00:49:27,490 --> 00:49:32,260
I prayed to be together with you and Dad again.

547
00:49:35,150 --> 00:49:36,520
Ah Rin, that's-

548
00:49:36,520 --> 00:49:40,110
Mom, is Dad not coming back?

549
00:49:40,950 --> 00:49:42,960
No.

550
00:49:42,960 --> 00:49:45,050
It's not like that.

551
00:49:49,190 --> 00:49:51,570
Can you please...

552
00:49:52,340 --> 00:49:57,230
give me just a little more time?

553
00:49:58,070 --> 00:50:00,920
I'll explain everything to you later.

554
00:50:05,800 --> 00:50:07,220
Thank you.

555
00:50:07,960 --> 00:50:10,610
Let's go. Thank you.

556
00:50:11,610 --> 00:50:13,300
Let's go.

557
00:50:25,280 --> 00:50:26,860
I said I'm fine.

558
00:50:26,860 --> 00:50:28,720
You're sure you're okay, right?

559
00:50:28,720 --> 00:50:30,990
Call me immediately if something happens.

560
00:50:32,270 --> 00:50:33,910
Okay.

561
00:50:46,890 --> 00:50:49,660
Long time no see, Nam Cheol.

562
00:50:49,660 --> 00:50:52,030
I was surprised to hear from you out of the blue.

563
00:50:52,030 --> 00:50:53,590
I know.

564
00:50:53,590 --> 00:50:57,580
I didn't think I'd be calling you directly.

565
00:50:57,580 --> 00:51:00,030
I wasn't so sure, actually.

566
00:51:00,030 --> 00:51:04,760
Considering what happened to Sun Yeong and what the articles said,

567
00:51:04,760 --> 00:51:07,920
I wasn't sure if I should be calling you or not.

568
00:51:09,770 --> 00:51:12,420
What did you want to see me for?

569
00:51:15,250 --> 00:51:18,260
Sun Yeong left this with me.

570
00:51:18,260 --> 00:51:21,130
He asked me to hold on to it just in case.

571
00:51:21,130 --> 00:51:22,350
Sun Yeong did?

572
00:51:22,350 --> 00:51:25,710
I didn't check to see what's in it.

573
00:51:25,710 --> 00:51:27,950
I thought that was the right thing to do.

574
00:51:32,580 --> 00:51:34,380
Thank you.

575
00:51:35,200 --> 00:51:36,680
I'll have a look at it.

576
00:51:36,680 --> 00:51:38,870
But you know...

577
00:51:38,870 --> 00:51:43,100
I'm not sure if I can tell you this, but...

578
00:51:43,880 --> 00:51:46,730
Sun Yeong was looking for...

579
00:51:46,730 --> 00:51:50,760
his daughter's biological father before he died.

580
00:51:58,120 --> 00:52:01,350
[USB Drive]

581
00:52:01,350 --> 00:52:04,100
[Audio file]

582
00:52:06,510 --> 00:52:08,500
Father.

583
00:52:08,500 --> 00:52:10,470
I need you to help me.

584
00:52:10,470 --> 00:52:12,760
S-Seung Gyu...

585
00:52:12,760 --> 00:52:15,620
Seung Gyu fell from the rooftop.

586
00:52:15,620 --> 00:52:19,260
It couldn't be helped because he threatened to kill us both.

587
00:52:20,490 --> 00:52:22,310
Is he dead?

588
00:52:23,900 --> 00:52:25,670
I don't know.

589
00:52:26,900 --> 00:52:29,170
Come home immediately.

590
00:52:38,510 --> 00:52:40,840
Is it true the Busan store is closing?

591
00:52:40,840 --> 00:52:42,930
You know that's the first Dereve store.

592
00:52:42,930 --> 00:52:44,950
Ms. Seo put the most effort into that one.

593
00:52:44,950 --> 00:52:46,700
So what?

594
00:52:46,700 --> 00:52:49,350
The sales dropped the most there.

595
00:52:49,350 --> 00:52:53,180
We might need to reduce the workforce if this doesn't work.

596
00:52:54,200 --> 00:52:55,610
Ms. Seo is definitely coming back.

597
00:52:55,610 --> 00:52:57,990
She wasn't acquitted yet

598
00:52:57,990 --> 00:53:00,770
and everyone's still criticizing her.

599
00:53:01,530 --> 00:53:03,660
How would she justify coming back?

600
00:53:12,040 --> 00:53:13,190
[Is Seo Jae Won mentally ill? She displayed self-harm since her school days.]

601
00:53:13,190 --> 00:53:15,170
Tell her if you get to meet her.

602
00:53:15,170 --> 00:53:19,070
It might look better if she steps down herself.

603
00:53:19,940 --> 00:53:22,420
We have to save the company, at least.

604
00:53:32,790 --> 00:53:35,210
What are the directors's reactions?

605
00:53:35,210 --> 00:53:36,650
They're feeling uneasy.

606
00:53:36,650 --> 00:53:39,200
To be honest, it's not good.

607
00:53:40,150 --> 00:53:42,220
The headlines have been so negative.

608
00:53:42,220 --> 00:53:43,880
But they were already disapproved.

609
00:53:43,880 --> 00:53:45,550
I know, but...

610
00:53:45,550 --> 00:53:49,980
the issue is that it led to Dereve's decline in sales.

611
00:53:49,980 --> 00:53:51,580
You know how the shareholders are.

612
00:53:51,580 --> 00:53:56,620
They don't care who the CEO is as long as they make them money.

613
00:53:56,620 --> 00:53:59,400
If that's the case, it wouldn't be a problem at all.

614
00:54:00,900 --> 00:54:02,620
Would it be possible?

615
00:54:02,620 --> 00:54:06,950
Ms. Seo might not be able to right now.

616
00:54:06,950 --> 00:54:08,580
We should give it a try.

617
00:54:11,900 --> 00:54:14,090
Chairman Kwon Yeong Ik is using Director Park

618
00:54:14,090 --> 00:54:17,670
to get the shareholders to vote for your dismissal.

619
00:54:17,670 --> 00:54:21,570
You need to decline the summon and try to come up with a solution-

620
00:54:21,570 --> 00:54:23,250
Te Oh.

621
00:54:24,420 --> 00:54:25,830
Yes.

622
00:54:27,980 --> 00:54:30,800
Would declining mean anything?

623
00:54:32,310 --> 00:54:34,650
You said there are articles about my illness, right?

624
00:54:34,650 --> 00:54:38,370
They said they stopped Reporter Choi from publishing it.

625
00:54:41,670 --> 00:54:44,550
What if they're right?

626
00:54:47,520 --> 00:54:52,400
It's true that I'm causing harm to Dereve.

627
00:54:53,370 --> 00:54:56,330
It's also true that I'm suffering from a mental illness.

628
00:54:56,330 --> 00:54:59,520
The articles can come out anytime.

629
00:54:59,520 --> 00:55:01,600
No, that won't happen.

630
00:55:01,600 --> 00:55:03,890
I'll prevent it from now on.

631
00:55:13,080 --> 00:55:14,610
Yes, Attorney.

632
00:55:14,610 --> 00:55:18,670
Ms. Seo, the first autopsy report came out.

633
00:55:22,050 --> 00:55:23,920
I heard Heo Sun Yeong's autopsy report came out.

634
00:55:23,920 --> 00:55:25,220
Yes.

635
00:55:26,040 --> 00:55:27,500
Here you go.

636
00:55:30,220 --> 00:55:31,440
Shit.

637
00:55:31,440 --> 00:55:34,950
Didn't the smartwatch say 1:42?
[Autopsy Report]

638
00:55:34,950 --> 00:55:36,300
Yes.

639
00:55:37,360 --> 00:55:39,400
W-When did you get here?

640
00:55:39,400 --> 00:55:43,070
The autopsy report says 10 p.m. to 1 a.m.

641
00:55:44,800 --> 00:55:46,600
How funny, right?

642
00:55:53,590 --> 00:55:56,570
This is your share of Dereve's stock.

643
00:55:57,440 --> 00:55:59,220
Attend the shareholders' meeting tomorrow.

644
00:55:59,220 --> 00:56:01,850
You just need to do as I say.

645
00:56:02,900 --> 00:56:06,100
Why don't you just do it on your own

646
00:56:06,100 --> 00:56:08,360
instead of telling me, then?

647
00:56:08,360 --> 00:56:11,300
Because you need to attend, at least.

648
00:56:11,300 --> 00:56:14,880
Shouldn't you prove your worth now?

649
00:56:16,060 --> 00:56:19,820
You abandoned your precious Seo Jae Won, too.

650
00:56:19,820 --> 00:56:23,940
What would be the point for me to prove it?

651
00:56:23,940 --> 00:56:29,000
You had everything just because you're my daughter.

652
00:56:29,000 --> 00:56:37,200
Remember that everything you have comes from me.

653
00:56:45,720 --> 00:56:47,520
[Dereve's First Shareholders' Meeting]

654
00:56:53,810 --> 00:56:55,860
[Kwon Yeong Ik]

655
00:56:55,860 --> 00:56:58,330
[Seo Jae Won]

656
00:57:05,480 --> 00:57:07,370
What are you doing here?

657
00:57:07,370 --> 00:57:11,010
Didn't you know I'm Dereve's shareholder?

658
00:57:11,010 --> 00:57:15,130
I'm a shareholder of this company, thanks to my capable father.

659
00:57:19,470 --> 00:57:21,240
How does it feel?

660
00:57:21,240 --> 00:57:25,570
You killed the man you loved, framed your friend,

661
00:57:25,570 --> 00:57:28,270
and you have her company now.

662
00:57:28,270 --> 00:57:30,100
Yeah.

663
00:57:30,100 --> 00:57:32,460
I feel great.

664
00:57:32,460 --> 00:57:36,050
Because I'd be seeing Seo Jae Won getting kicked out of Dereve.

665
00:57:36,980 --> 00:57:41,930
It turns out you're such a pitiful person.

666
00:57:43,260 --> 00:57:45,480
You'd better watch what you say.

667
00:57:45,480 --> 00:57:47,010
Watch carefully.

668
00:57:47,010 --> 00:57:52,130
It's all you who ruined yourself like this. Not Seo Jae Won.

669
00:57:53,080 --> 00:57:55,670
How much further must you fall to realize that?

670
00:57:55,670 --> 00:57:58,500
How about you? Why Seo Jae Won?

671
00:57:58,500 --> 00:58:02,860
She wasn't by your side when you were lost and struggled.

672
00:58:02,860 --> 00:58:05,330
I'm the one who was by your side then.

673
00:58:05,330 --> 00:58:06,780
You're right.

674
00:58:08,520 --> 00:58:11,050
That's been stopping me all this time.

675
00:58:11,900 --> 00:58:14,590
But I'll cut you off without lingering feelings.

676
00:58:15,550 --> 00:58:18,810
Even if I have to cut off my ankle.

677
00:58:20,730 --> 00:58:23,990
That way, I'd be able to pay you back.

678
00:58:27,030 --> 00:58:28,840
Hang in there for a bit.

679
00:58:34,640 --> 00:58:37,430
Do you know what I regret the most?

680
00:58:38,460 --> 00:58:41,820
Holding your hand when you wanted to die seven years ago.

681
00:58:44,560 --> 00:58:46,570
What you said just now...

682
00:58:50,180 --> 00:58:52,100
is very hurtful.

683
00:58:53,530 --> 00:58:57,280
I wanted to be understood by you a tiny bit.

684
00:59:00,580 --> 00:59:02,770
I guess I was asking for too much.

685
00:59:24,800 --> 00:59:26,410
Su Gyeong.

686
00:59:27,280 --> 00:59:29,980
I'm sorry for making a difficult request.

687
00:59:29,980 --> 00:59:32,400
Let's have dinner together afterward.

688
00:59:43,180 --> 00:59:45,620
[Dereve Shareholders' Meeting]

689
00:59:51,360 --> 00:59:54,440
[Seo Jae Won]

690
00:59:56,040 --> 00:59:58,900
Doctor, you have a visitor.

691
00:59:58,900 --> 01:00:01,800
Didn't I mention I have no appointments this morning?

692
01:00:01,800 --> 01:00:06,570
It's not that. He's here because of Ms. Seo Jae Won.

693
01:00:06,570 --> 01:00:09,700
- Hello, Doctor.
- Oh, yes. Hello

694
01:00:09,700 --> 01:00:13,230
I'm Yoon Te Oh, Dereve's design team leader.

695
01:00:13,230 --> 01:00:15,130
Oh, I see.

696
01:00:15,130 --> 01:00:18,080
You're here regarding Ms. Seo Jae Won?

697
01:00:18,080 --> 01:00:19,350
Yes.

698
01:00:19,350 --> 01:00:24,490
Ms. Seo asked me to come. You don't have to hide it from me.

699
01:00:26,540 --> 01:00:29,390
What did she ask you to do?

700
01:00:29,390 --> 01:00:33,770
I heard you're her psychiatrist and a friend.

701
01:00:35,460 --> 01:00:37,130
Me?

702
01:00:37,980 --> 01:00:39,210
Aren't you?

703
01:00:39,210 --> 01:00:44,060
I d-don't have a personal relationship with Ms. Seo.

704
01:00:44,060 --> 01:00:47,490
I-I've never even met her.

705
01:00:47,490 --> 01:00:51,210
Looks like you're mistaken.

706
01:00:52,970 --> 01:00:56,830
No, no. There's no way, Te Oh.

707
01:01:02,770 --> 01:01:04,520
Okay.

708
01:01:23,710 --> 01:01:24,920
Flower therapy. Have you heard of it?

709
01:01:24,920 --> 01:01:27,320
According to a study, the scent of flowers reduces stress...

710
01:01:27,320 --> 01:01:30,090
You heal just by smelling.

711
01:01:36,070 --> 01:01:39,600
Your husband, father, and Yun Te Oh...

712
01:01:39,600 --> 01:01:41,890
Is that man...

713
01:01:41,890 --> 01:01:45,460
How about other people's situations?

714
01:01:45,460 --> 01:01:49,990
They might not have anything to do with me...

715
01:01:49,990 --> 01:01:52,430
You want to believe it's not true, right?

716
01:01:53,480 --> 01:01:55,640
Why didn't you take the medicine?

717
01:01:55,640 --> 01:01:57,600
There was an important presentation.

718
01:01:57,600 --> 01:01:59,400
I thought a few days would be fine.

719
01:01:59,400 --> 01:02:01,480
You should accept it now.

720
01:02:01,480 --> 01:02:06,190
Your relationship with Heo Sun Yeong is over.

721
01:02:12,160 --> 01:02:13,810
Su Gyeong.

722
01:02:14,810 --> 01:02:17,480
I'm sorry for making a difficult request.

723
01:02:17,480 --> 01:02:20,640
Let's have dinner together afterward.

724
01:02:20,640 --> 01:02:23,780
The number you dialed does not exist.

725
01:02:23,780 --> 01:02:26,770
Please check and dial again.

726
01:02:57,600 --> 01:02:59,590
Just one moment.

727
01:03:07,690 --> 01:03:09,970
I'm different from Mom.

728
01:03:11,170 --> 01:03:14,220
I'll never end things this way.

729
01:03:15,520 --> 01:03:19,180
♫ Why would it happen? ♫

730
01:03:19,180 --> 01:03:23,180
♫ Like how it all has been connected ♫

731
01:03:23,180 --> 01:03:26,960
♫ Only if I don't ♫

732
01:03:26,960 --> 01:03:30,070
♫ In between the empty darkness ♫

733
01:03:30,070 --> 01:03:37,800
♫ I wanna know. You blow in. ♫

734
01:03:37,800 --> 01:03:46,070
♫ I wanna know ♫

735
01:03:46,070 --> 01:03:50,090
♫ I'm not okay. I can feel your touch. ♫

736
01:03:50,090 --> 01:03:53,960
♫ A huge wave of memories are coming in ♫

737
01:03:53,960 --> 01:03:57,810
♫ I'm not okay. I can hear your voice. ♫

738
01:03:57,810 --> 01:04:03,810
♫ I picture us seeing each other in my dream ♫

739
01:04:03,810 --> 01:04:11,540
♫ The conclusion that had stalled along with the truth ♫

740
01:04:11,540 --> 01:04:15,440
♫ Would you look back ♫

741
01:04:15,440 --> 01:04:19,530
[My Happy Ending]

742
01:04:19,530 --> 01:04:21,870
Time to take your medicine, Ms. Seo Jae Won.

743
01:04:21,870 --> 01:04:25,320
I think I have a lot of things to do once I get discharged.

744
01:04:25,320 --> 01:04:28,000
I heard you'll be the artist for Dereve's project.

745
01:04:28,000 --> 01:04:31,290
Good luck with it. It's your company from now on, too.

746
01:04:31,290 --> 01:04:32,700
Please keep an eye on them.

747
01:04:32,700 --> 01:04:35,670
You never know what Kwon Yun Jin and Kwon Yeong Ik would do.

748
01:04:35,670 --> 01:04:37,850
I heard Heo Sun Yeong's case will have a new detective in charge.

749
01:04:37,850 --> 01:04:39,170
I think you should watch out.

750
01:04:39,170 --> 01:04:42,210
How could you use an innocent child as a shield?

751
01:04:42,210 --> 01:04:44,270
She was mine from the beginning.

752
01:04:44,270 --> 01:04:45,610
How should I take care of it?

753
01:04:45,610 --> 01:04:47,110
Let me manage it myself.

754
01:04:47,110 --> 01:04:53,190
I'm making plans and getting things done one by one starting now.
